    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with ASME V&V 40 Table 3 allowances at this risk level. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all 5 CPB operating points with mean NIH error of 8.3%, within the 15% acceptance criterion. The assessment team notes that solver configuration parameters (mesh density 0.15 mm, stress threshold τ_th = 50 Pa, convergence tolerance 1e-5) are described in the validation narrative and were used consistently across all V&V runs. The credibility package is accepted at Medium assurance level for the stated COU.",
